{"tid":1373313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發完夢點走","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:05:34.000Z","uid":122782,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb252c6c087b356aa3f4c80a43c65f27128eb0e2","tid":1373313,"uid":122782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要 幫手推!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n次次發完夢都見到一大班人係到排隊買飛<br />\n但係其實既然你買得飛入黎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你黎嗰陣係可以買一次過兩張飛，買晒來回</span></span><br />\n佢車飛<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無話你邊到買就要邊到入</span><br />\n佢張飛只會計你夠唔夠錢俾個車程<br />\n所以其實你張車飛係可以係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">任何一個站入都得</span><br />\n只係你出閘個陣有可能唔夠錢要去CS補錢 (多咗錢就無咩所謂)<br />\n所以唔該大家以後出去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接買兩張飛，直接買來回</span></span><br />\n派飛嘅都唔洗專登講張飛去邊一區啦，走個陣入咗閘上咗車先算啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要 好多人唔知 幫手推!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"dcbedb48b1aa8374f2a29fb0cd1434c422a64b36","tid":1373313,"uid":122782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e608780dfec002300632080fa042f26660481d1e","tid":1373313,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"係時候成立民間防衛隊做返警察應該做嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n依家咁多證據都證明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">警察=黑社會</span></span>，依家嘅警察已經失去合法性<br />\n<br />\n首先可以由集體唔交稅開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7XMWCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7XMWCx.png&h=73fa9ee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f8d69685119f6be1d3c88da84755cabb9e82e34","tid":1373313,"uid":122782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"ef62fda6d3b74ac91c2ac7c5ec3ac4f035a1d00c","tid":1373313,"uid":122782,"like"